snippet: The lawmaker, Sergey Vlasenko, is a close associate of former Prime Minister Yulia V. Tymoshenko, who has been jailed.
abstract: Ukraine's top administrative court strips Sergey Vlasenko of his seat in Parliament in what Western officials call a matter of political retribution; Vlasenko is the lead defender for jailed former Prime Min Yulia V Tymoshenko.
lead_paragraph: The lawmaker, Sergey Vlasenko, is a close associate of former Prime Minister Yulia V. Tymoshenko, who has been jailed.

headline.seo: In Ukraine, Tymoshenko Ally Ousted From Parliament
headline.main: Ex-Premier’s Ally Expelled From Ukraine Parliament
headline.print_headline: Ex-Premier’s Ally Expelled From Ukraine Parliament
